HEADWORD: Balancer
<hw>Bal"an*cer</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who balances, or uses a balance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>In Diptera, the rudimentary
